{"tid":938263,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"恐懼和短視，係咪先係人類幸福和發展的黑星","createTime":"2018-12-12T07:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T10:36:22.000Z","uid":149978,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9fc878b2fbe33dd0cad52fb7779948e76da4e4f0","tid":938263,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:20:00.000Z","msg":"好似目前的科技革命<br />\n如人工智能，超級機械人，3D列印咁<br />\n明明係用黎做福人群<br />\n減少人類從事低價值工作（例如重復性高、厭惡性、奴性重的工作）<br />\n推動人類整體從事更高價值工作。<br />\n既能提高人類生產力，又能減少體力和勞力勞動，仲可以更環保和安全。<br />\n絕對係提升人類尊嚴的好科技。<br />\n<br />\n但就被人類講成係機械人取代人類，科技恐懼。<br />\n講到人類的尊嚴盡失咁。<br />\n雖然係短期內有班工友因無法轉型而失業，<br />\n但長遠一定係好事，提高人類尊嚴、健康和幸福。<br />\n<br />\n短視和恐懼的人，睇乜都咁負面。<br />\n好野都當成壞東西。"},{"pid":"54b8de4ac90c3e94b4cdba16e3c63d51221a6911","tid":938263,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:20:50.000Z","msg":"真正的奴性重。"},{"pid":"a3759874762554ce30f67126cbc6d961a813d1f2","tid":938263,"uid":22624,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:24:43.000Z","msg":"剋星"},{"pid":"667292dc60ca3085c043abb2bcb23ea735937857","tid":938263,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:25:53.000Z","msg":"基因工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf95d332c5cb251fdeecbf86688c7c9629e4fef2","tid":938263,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"667292dc60ca3085c043abb2bcb23ea735937857","tid":938263,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:25:53.000Z","msg":"基因工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:27:15.000Z","msg":"人類得八十歲命，世界紀錄最長壽122歲。<br />\n只有靠基因工程才有望突破極限。"},{"pid":"63dbebff3bbec80e33e827873293135099b892ff","tid":938263,"uid":51021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:53:19.000Z","msg":"租哥先係人類幸福既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">剋</span></spa